---
// src/pages/index.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Isaak Simpson - Outdoor Sustainability Projects">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-900/70 to-slate-900/90 z-10"></div>
        <img 
          src="/images/feature-photo.webp" 
          alt="Scenic mountain landscape" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
      
      <!-- Hero Content -->
      <div class="relative z-20 container mx-auto px-4 h-screen flex flex-col justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
            <span class="block text-emerald-400">Reconnect</span>
            with nature through sustainable products
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-200 mb-10">
            Discover my initiatives that preserve wild spaces while creating immersive outdoor experiences for all.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-emerald-500 text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-all hover:bg-emerald-600 shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-500/30">
              <span>Explore Projects</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-all hover:bg-white/10">
              Learn More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-20 animate-bounce">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <img src="/images/solar-garden.jpg" alt="Sustainability in action" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl" />
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6">My Commitment to the Wild</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
              I believe that outdoor exploration and environmental stewardship go hand in hand. My initiatives focus on creating sustainable adventure opportunities while preserving natural ecosystems for future generations.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
                <div class="bg-emerald-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Sustainable Trails</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Building and maintaining eco-friendly trails that minimize environmental impact.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
                <div class="bg-emerald-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Education Programs</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Teaching outdoor skills while fostering environmental awareness and responsibility.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-emerald-900 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Community Impact</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-emerald-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Hear from fellow industy experts on the impact Isaak is making.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-800 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-emerald-300 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M10 11l-4 4v-7l4 3zm6-3v7l-4-4 4-3z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-emerald-100">
            "Isaak brings a rare blend of creativity, technical skill, and environmental awareness to sustainable product design. His work reflects a deep commitment to creating thoughtful, nature-inspired solutions that are both functional and future-minded. Whether it's rethinking materials or reimagining everyday products with a lighter footprint, Isaak consistently delivers designs that are innovative, responsible, and inspiring."            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="font-bold text-xl">J</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Jamie Torres</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-300 text-sm">TechTex Solutions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
          <div class="bg-emerald-800 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-emerald-300 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M10 11l-4 4v-7l4 3zm6-3v7l-4-4 4-3z" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-emerald-100">
              "Isaak approaches sustainable product design with genuine passion and a sharp problem-solving mindset. His ability to balance aesthetic appeal with eco-conscious materials and processes makes his work stand out. He doesn't just design for todayâ€”he designs with tomorrow in mind, making a real impact in the push for a more sustainable future."
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="font-bold text-xl">M</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Morgan Chen</h4>
                <p class="text-emerald-300 text-sm">Conservation Director @ EnergyReturn</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-teal-600 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8">
            Discover our outdoor sustainability projects and find ways to participate or support our initiatives.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/projects" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-emerald-700 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all hover:bg-emerald-50 shadow-lg hover:shadow-white/30"
          >
            <span>Explore All Projects</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>